<P>
PRENATAL CARE ORDER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 As a result of Wilson's executive order denying prenatal care to illegal 
mothers, many a child may be born with physical or mental defects. Since any 
child born in the United States is a citizen, these children are entitled to 
taxpayer-financed social services.  
</P>
<P>
 G. BORDING MATHIEU 
</P>
<P>
 Laguna Beach 
</P>
