<DOCNO> LA111694-0054 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 099025 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 16, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
