"Gingrich just accused Tiny Tim of faking his leg injury to get workers' comp." 
</P>
<P>
 Ray says conservative Republicans plan to unveil their new health plan for the 
aged: "Sleep it off." 
</P>
<P>
 Leno, on "The Flintstones," now out on home video: "The Flintstones wear fur, 
eat red meat and have this Stone Age philosophy. So technically, they were the 
first Republicans." 
</P>
<P>
 Rep. Dick Armey, likely to become the next House majority leader, says the GOP 
isn't out to get revenge, because "you cannot get ahead when you're getting 
even." Says comedy writer Tony Peyser: "Boy, this guy wouldn't last a week in 
Hollywood." 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
