state elections. He asked Sam if he knew the name of the state they lived in. 
Sam, needing a hint, asked what letter the word started with. " Ca . . . " his 
father began, hoping to jog his memory. 
</P>
<P>
 Sam thought a while , then replied, " . . . wabunga?"  
</P>
