<DOCNO> LA111694-0137 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 099108 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 16, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 4; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
