<TEXT>
<P>
 Jennifer Hodges 
</P>
<P>
 SCHOOL: Chatsworth 
</P>
<P>
 SPORT: Volleyball 
</P>
<P>
 YEAR: Senior 
</P>
<P>
 SEASON AT A GLANCE: Hodges, a 6-foot middle blocker, has been one of the 
Chancellors' most consistent hitters. Chatsworth was undefeated in Northwest 
Valley Conference play until the final match of the regular season and shared 
the conference title with El Camino Real. 
</P>
