 High Schools 
</P>
<P>
 The state Department of Education on Tuesday released data comparing how high 
schools are preparing their students for college. The report includes scores 
for 55 schools in the Los Angeles Unified School District as well as a 
comparison score for other schools statewide with similar student populations. 
