<TEXT>
<P>
 Jim Murray -- A reference in Sunday's column to Ara Parseghian's last game as 
Notre Dame's coach being a 55-24 loss to USC was in error. Parseghian's last 
game was a 13-11 victory over Alabama in the Orange Bowl on Jan. 1, 1975. 
</P>
